data.description: Welcome to your charming and refined retreat at this 3 bedroom 2 bath 2 garage full brick home situated on OVER 1/2 an acre. Step inside to the open living room with the well-appointed kitchen with walk in pantry and formal dining area perfect for both intimate dinners and lively gatherings. Retreat to the primary suite with his and hers walk in deep closets, stunning tray ceilings and master ensuite bathroom with a deep soaking tub and dual sinks. 2 Additional well maintained bedrooms, full laundry room and second full bathroom. Outside, the expansive full privacy fence with no neighbors behind just a wooded treeline providing your own personal sanctuary for outdoor enjoyment. Enjoy the community amenities- pool, playground or take a nice stroll down the neighborhood on the sidewalks. This home awaits you!
